PICOs.Population: Adult patients with advanced non-small cell lung cancer (NSCLC) with KRAS G12C mutation who have progressed after at least one prior systemic therapy.
PICOs.Outcomes: Progression-free survival (PFS), overall survival (OS), safety, quality of life, cost per QALY
